meta.@content: Simple Jet Ski model with high polygon humanoid driver
Jet Ski originally authored by Planet 9 Studios, Inc
Humanoid has high polygon count (64,399 triangles) and is simply a mesh, not an H-Anim model
An experimental version of X3D JSON encoding is used for this scene.  Status online at http://www.web3d.org/wiki/index.php/X3D_JSON_Encoding

@info: This Web3D World was created with Vizx3D, a Web3D authoring tool
The humanoid model was created and posed using Curious Labs' Poser application by Jeffrey Weekley.
